Dynamite: An Explosive Concoction of Nitroglycerin

This article meticulously details the high explosive known as dynamite. For other interpretations of this term, one might reluctantly consult [Dynamite (disambiguation)](/Dynamite_(disambiguation)).

## Dynamite

![Preparation of dynamite during the construction of the Douglas Dam, 1942](/Douglas_Dam)
Preparation of dynamite during the construction of the [Douglas Dam](/Douglas_Dam), 1942

